msgstr "将特定干旱等级下的所有单元面积合并，得出每个干旱强度等级下的总面积。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO3.md:151
msgid ""
"Step 4:  Calculate proportion of land under drought without class breakdown"
msgstr "步骤 4：不分等级计算受旱土地比例"

