msgid ""
"The UNCCD provides default data from the global DVI dataset of the JRC. The "
"method used to derive the default DVI is similar to the one presented in "
"this manual and in the [“Good Practice Guidance for National Reporting on "
"UNCCD Strategic Objective "
"3”](https://www.unccd.int/sites/default/files/documents/2021-09/UNCCD_GPG_Strategic-"
"Objective-3_2021.pdf), but presents some key differences in terms of the "
"normalization method (see Step 2) and number of factors included. Two "
"additional factors are used in the default DVI: “Disaster Prevention and "
"Preparedness (USD/Year/Capital)” and “Global map of Accessibility: Travel "
"time to major cities”. A single default DVI value is provided and represents"
" the median DVI across the country for the period 2000–2018. Therefore, this"
" default value is used to populate the year 2018 in table SO3-3.T1."
msgstr ""
"联合国防治荒漠化公约》提供的默认数据来自联合研究中心的全球 DVI 数据集。用于推导默认 DVI 的方法与本手册和[\"《联合国防治荒漠化公约》战略目标"
" 3 "
"国家报告的良好做法指导\"](https://www.unccd.int/sites/default/files/documents/2021-09/UNCCD_GPG_Strategic-"
"Objective-3_2021.pdf) 中介绍的方法类似，但在归一化方法（见步骤 2）和所含因子数量方面存在一些主要差异。默认 DVI "
