#: ../../SO3.md:577
msgid "Drought Vulnerability for the year 2000 or closest available year"
msgstr "2000 年或最接近的年份的干旱脆弱性"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO3.md:578
msgid "Drought Vulnerability for the year 2023 or closest available year"
msgstr "2023 年或最接近的年份的干旱脆弱性"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO3.md:580
msgid ""
"Information on data sources, data accuracy and any weighting scheme applied "
"to the vulnerability factors can be submitted using the “General Comments” "
"field. It would also be beneficial to report on special cases and issues, "
"describing situations where values might be less reliable and providing the "
"rationale for inclusion of different factors."
msgstr ""
"有关数据来源、数据准确性和脆弱性因素加权方案的信息可通过 \"一般评论 "
"\"栏提交。报告特殊情况和问题，说明数值可能不太可靠的情况，并提供纳入不同因素的理由，也会有所裨益。"

#: ../../SO3.md:584
msgid "3.3.4. Dependencies"
msgstr "3.3.4. 依赖性"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO3.md:586
msgid ""
"SO 2-1 and SO 2-2 can be used for the calculation of SO 3-3. This is "
"explained in the [Good Practice Guidance for National Reporting on UNCCD "
"Strategic Objective "
"3](https://www.unccd.int/sites/default/files/documents/2021-09/UNCCD_GPG_Strategic-"
"Objective-3_2021.pdf). Chapter 3. Level 3 Indicator."
msgstr ""
"SO 2-1 和 SO 2-2 可用于计算 SO 3-3。联合国防治荒漠化公约战略目标 3 "
"国家报告良好做法指南](https://www.unccd.int/sites/default/files/documents/2021-09/UNCCD_GPG_Strategic-"
"Objective-3_2021.pdf) 对此进行了解释。第 3 章.第 3 级指标。"

#: ../../SO3.md:588
msgid "3.3.5. Challenges"
msgstr "3.3.5. 挑战"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO3.md:592
msgid "The global DVI dataset of the JRC is only available for the year 2018."
msgstr "联合研究中心的全球 DVI 数据集仅提供 2018 年的数据。"

#: ../../SO3.md:593
msgid ""
"The availability of data for the considered factors varies substantially "
"from country to country and the complete set of recommended data might not "
"be accessible everywhere."
msgstr "有关所考虑系数的数据可用性在各国之间有很大差异，可能不是所有地方都能获得完整的建议数据。"

#: ../../SO3.md:595
msgid "Methodological approach"
msgstr "方法论"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO3.md:597
msgid ""
"The reliability of the DVI method at national and sub-national levels is "
"still to be verified by national experts."
msgstr "DVI 方法在国家和国家以下各级的可靠性仍有待国家专家验证。"

#: ../../SO3.md:599
msgid ""
"Due to the methods used for factor normalization (i.e., using in-country "
"historic data), DVI values should not be compared between countries."
msgstr "由于用于系数归一化的方法（即使用国内的历史数据）存在差异，不应在国家之间比较DVI值。"

#: ../../SO3.md:601
msgid ""
"Assuming a consistent methodology has been used over time, changes in the "
"DVI may reflect the efficacy of drought mitigation and adaptation policies, "
"but they may also reveal the impacts of social and economic changes "
"disconnected from drought management measures."
msgstr "假设长期使用一致的方法，DVI的变化可能反映干旱缓解和适应政策的有效性，但也可能揭示与干旱管理措施无关的社会和经济变化的影响。"

#: ../../SO3.md:603
msgid "3.3.6. Summary (main actions)"
msgstr "3.3.6. 总结（主要行动）"

#: ../../SO3.md:605
msgid ""
"Key actions for reporting population vulnerable to drought hazard are as "
"follows:"
msgstr "报告易受干旱灾害的人口时需采取的关键行动如下："

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO3.md:607
msgid ""
"**Select tier of vulnerability assessment based on data availability**: "
"Parties are encouraged to opt for one of the three Tiers of VA based on data"
" availability. In the absence of data to calculate the minimum Tier 1 VA, "
"Parties may use the default data. National/regional data products used to "
"calculate the DVI should comply with the specifications listed in table 21. "
"If Parties use national/regional data products, they should follow actions 2"
" to 4 below:"
msgstr ""
"**根据现有数据选择脆弱性评估等级**：鼓励缔约方根据数据的可得性选择三个脆弱性评估等级中的一个。在没有数据计算最低第 1 "
"级脆弱性评估的情况下，缔约方可使用默认数据。用于计算 DVI 的国家/地区数据产品应符合表 21 "
"中列出的规格。如果缔约方使用国家/区域数据产品，则应遵循以下行动 2 至 4："

#: ../../SO3.md:609
msgid ""
"**Factor normalization**: factors for each vulnerability component should be"
" normalized before they can be compared and aggregated, as the vulnerability"
" factors used are all measured using different units."
msgstr "**系数归一化**：由于使用的脆弱性系数都是用不同的单位来衡量的，每个脆弱性成分的系数都应归一化，然后才能进行比较和汇总。"

#: ../../SO3.md:611
msgid ""
"**Derive the DVI components**: the aggregated values for each of the three "
"DVI components are calculated as the arithmetic mean of the normalized "
"factors."
msgstr "**得出DVI成分**：三个DVI成分中每一个成分的合计值都按照归一化系数的算术平均值计算。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO3.md:613
msgid ""
"**Calculate the DVI**: the three components – social, economic and "
"infrastructural – derived in the previous steps are used to produce the "
"annual DVI values by calculating their arithmetic mean value."
msgstr "**计算 DVI**：通过计算前几个步骤得出的社会、经济和基础设施三个组成部分的算术平均 值，得出年度 DVI 值。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO3.md:615
msgid ""
"**Report factors used to calculate DVI**: When national data is used to "
"complete table SO3-3.T1, Parties should also report on the factors used in "
"the calculation."
msgstr "**报告用于计算 DVI 的系数**：在使用国家数据完成表 SO3-3.T1 时，缔约方还应报告计算中使用的系数。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO3.md:617
msgid ""
"**Verify the results**: aware of the fact that the DVI method has not yet "
"been validated at the local or national scale, Parties should verify the "
"appropriateness of the default factors and add relevant ones as needed "
"before officially submitting estimates for UNCCD reporting."
msgstr ""
"**核实结果**：意识到 DVI "
"方法尚未在地方或国家范围内得到验证，缔约方应核实默认系数的适当性，并在正式提交《防治荒漠化公约》报告估算值之前，根据需要添加相关系数。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO3.md:619
msgid ""
"**Save form and make available for review**: once verified by the Parties, "
"the data and supporting narrative for the period assessed should be marked "
"as “In Review” and saved thereby making it available for review by the "
"UNCCD."
msgstr "**保存表格并提供审查**：经缔约方核实后，应将评估期间的数据和佐证说明标记为 \"审 查中 \"并保存，以便《荒漠化公约》审查。"

